title: Smoke's Poutinerie with Alana Johnston (LIVE)
itunes:title: Smoke's Poutinerie with Alana Johnston (LIVE)
description:
The 'boys are joined in snowy Saskatoon by Alana "The Knife" Johnston (The Birthday Boys, UCB) to review a chain set on spreading one of Canada's quintessential foods to the world: Smoke's Poutinerie. Plus, a live edition of Snack or Wack.

Recorded live at The Broadway Theatre in Saskatoon, Saskatchewan.

Want more Doughboys? Check out our Patreon!: https://patreon.com/doughboys
